    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join The Priest and The Hero on a wild adventure, where your decisions shape the fate of our brave (and occasionally clueless) heroes.  <br>With over 75 unique endings to discover, it’s up to you to guide them through every possible fate!  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>+75 Endings to discover</strong></u><strong>:</strong> The ultimate goal is to see how many different fates you can uncover. Each choice opens new branches and unexpected outcomes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213800/extras/4c45da03f3a24b726d182786750911d1.poster.avif?t=1771878148\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213800/extras/4c45da03f3a24b726d182786750911d1.webm?t=1771878148\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213800/extras/4c45da03f3a24b726d182786750911d1.mp4?t=1771878148\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Choices matter</strong></u><strong>:</strong> Cast spells, use items at critical moments, talk to enemies mid-battle, or make questionable decisions. Even small actions can radically change the story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213800/extras/c8951f1c80da4b5a982ae3a6fb827b27.poster.avif?t=1771878148\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213800/extras/c8951f1c80da4b5a982ae3a6fb827b27.webm?t=1771878148\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213800/extras/c8951f1c80da4b5a982ae3a6fb827b27.mp4?t=1771878148\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Progress That Carries Over</strong></u><strong>:</strong> Items and magic persist between runs, unlocking new options and paths. The more you play, the deeper the story becomes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213800/extras/48ca24062fa0ad300ec895928c4a3840.poster.avif?t=1771878148\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213800/extras/48ca24062fa0ad300ec895928c4a3840.webm?t=1771878148\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213800/extras/48ca24062fa0ad300ec895928c4a3840.mp4?t=1771878148\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Secrets Everywhere</strong></u><strong>: </strong>Every corner hides something new. Hidden interactions, unexpected outcomes, and secrets waiting to be discovered.</p></li></ul>",
